By: Sri Ramana Maharshi
---
Therefore we say that the Self-Realised Sage knows by his mind, but his mind
is pure. Again we say that the vibrating mind is impure and the placid mind
is pure. The pure mind is itself Brahma; therefore it follows that Brahma
is nought other than the mind of the sage.
